  "detailed_description": "GridMath is a challenging mathematical puzzle where you need to find a space in the grid for each number.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The challenges are divided into 5 blocks with 20 levels each.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play the levels of each block in the sequence you want.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose between different colors to play at any time.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>20 achievements to achieve.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You only need the mouse to play.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There is no timer, just relax and complete all levels in your time.</li></ul><br>Good luck!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1451300/extras/0ab1509e2d67178c0b90884babc675cc.avif?t=1604867706\" width=456 height=468 /></span>",
